var book = {
	"name": "2 Corinthians",
	"numChapters": 13,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>Paul, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28802A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28802A\"></sup>an apostle of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28802B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28802B\"></sup>Christ Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28802C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28802C\"></sup>by the will of God, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28802D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28802D\"></sup>Timothy <i>our</i> brother,To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28802E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28802E\"></sup>the church of God which is at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28802F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28802F\"></sup>Corinth with all the saints who are throughout <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28802G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28802G\"></sup>Achaia:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28803H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28803H\"></sup>Grace to you and peace from God our Father and the Lord Jesus Christ.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28804I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28804I\"></sup>Blessed <i>be</i> the God and Father of our Lord Jesus Christ, the Father of mercies and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28804J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28804J\"></sup>God of all comfort,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28805K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28805K\"></sup>comforts us in all our affliction so that we will be able to comfort those who are in any affliction with the comfort with which we ourselves are comforted by God.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For just <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28806L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28806L\"></sup>as the sufferings of Christ are ours in abundance, so also our comfort is abundant through Christ.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But if we are afflicted, it is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28807M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28807M\"></sup>for your comfort and salvation; or if we are comforted, it is for your comfort, which is effective in the patient enduring of the same sufferings which we also suffer;",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>and our hope for you is firmly grounded, knowing that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28808N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28808N\"></sup>as you are sharers of our sufferings, so also you are <i>sharers</i> of our comfort.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28809O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28809O\"></sup>we do not want you to be unaware, brethren, of our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28809P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28809P\"></sup>affliction which came <i>to us</i> in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28809Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28809Q\"></sup>Asia, that we were burdened excessively, beyond our strength, so that we despaired even of life;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>indeed, we had the sentence of death within ourselves so that we would not trust in ourselves, but in God who raises the dead;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28811R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28811R\"></sup>delivered us from so great a <i>peril of</i> death, and will deliver <i>us</i>, He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28811S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28811S\"></sup>on whom we have set our hope. And He will yet deliver us,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>you also joining in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28812T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28812T\"></sup>helping us through your prayers, so that thanks may be given by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28812U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28812U\"></sup>many persons on our behalf for the favor bestowed on us through <i>the prayers of</i> many.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For our proud confidence is this: the testimony of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28813V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28813V\"></sup>our conscience, that in holiness and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28813W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28813W\"></sup>godly sincerity, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28813X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28813X\"></sup>not in fleshly wisdom but in the grace of God, we have conducted ourselves in the world, and especially toward you.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For we write nothing else to you than what you read and understand, and I hope you will understand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28814Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28814Y\"></sup>until the end;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>just as you also partially did understand us, that we are your reason to be proud as you also are ours, in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28815Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28815Z\"></sup>the day of our Lord Jesus.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>In this confidence I intended at first to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28816AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28816AA\"></sup>come to you, so that you might twice receive a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28816AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28816AB\"></sup>blessing;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>that is, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28817AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28817AC\"></sup>pass your way into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28817AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28817AD\"></sup>Macedonia, and again from Macedonia to come to you, and by you to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28817AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28817AE\"></sup>helped on my journey to Judea.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Therefore, I was not vacillating when I intended to do this, was I? Or what I purpose, do I purpose <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28818AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28818AF\"></sup>according to the flesh, so that with me there will be yes, yes and no, no <i>at the same time</i>?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28819AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28819AG\"></sup>God is faithful, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28819AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28819AH\"></sup>our word to you is not yes and no.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28820AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28820AI\"></sup>the Son of God, Christ Jesus, who was preached among you by us—by me and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28820AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28820AJ\"></sup>Silvanus and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28820AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28820AK\"></sup>Timothy—was not yes and no, but is yes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28820AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28820AL\"></sup>in Him.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28821AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28821AM\"></sup>as many as are the promises of God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28821AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28821AN\"></sup>in Him they are yes; therefore also through Him is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28821AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28821AO\"></sup>our Amen to the glory of God through us.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Now He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28822AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28822AP\"></sup>establishes us with you in Christ and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28822AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28822AQ\"></sup>anointed us is God,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>who also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28823AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28823AR\"></sup>sealed us and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28823AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28823AS\"></sup>gave <i>us</i> the Spirit in our hearts as a pledge.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28824AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28824AT\"></sup>I call God as witness to my soul, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28824AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28824AU\"></sup>to spare you I did not come again to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28824AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28824AV\"></sup>Corinth.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Not that we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28825AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28825AW\"></sup>lord it over your faith, but are workers with you for your joy; for in your faith you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28825AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28825AX\"></sup>standing firm."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>But I determined this for my own sake, that I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28826A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28826A\"></sup>would not come to you in sorrow again.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For if I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28827B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28827B\"></sup>cause you sorrow, who then makes me glad but the one whom I made sorrowful?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>This is the very thing I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28828C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28828C\"></sup>wrote you, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28828D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28828D\"></sup>when I came, I would not have sorrow from those who ought to make me rejoice; having <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28828E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28828E\"></sup>confidence in you all that my joy would be <i>the joy</i> of you all.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For out of much affliction and anguish of heart I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28829F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28829F\"></sup>wrote to you with many tears; not so that you would be made sorrowful, but that you might know the love which I have especially for you.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28830G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28830G\"></sup>if any has caused sorrow, he has caused sorrow not to me, but in some degree—in order not to say too much—to all of you.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Sufficient for such a one is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28831H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28831H\"></sup>this punishment which <i>was inflicted</i> by the majority,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>so that on the contrary you should rather <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28832I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28832I\"></sup>forgive and comfort <i>him</i>, otherwise such a one might be overwhelmed by excessive sorrow.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Wherefore I urge you to reaffirm <i>your</i> love for him.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For to this end also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28834J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28834J\"></sup>I wrote, so that I might <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28834K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28834K\"></sup>put you to the test, whether you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28834L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28834L\"></sup>obedient in all things.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But one whom you forgive anything, I <i>forgive</i> also; for indeed what I have forgiven, if I have forgiven anything, <i>I did it</i> for your sakes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28835M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28835M\"></sup>in the presence of Christ,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>so that no advantage would be taken of us by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28836N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28836N\"></sup>Satan, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28836O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28836O\"></sup>we are not ignorant of his schemes.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Now when I came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28837P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28837P\"></sup>Troas for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28837Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28837Q\"></sup>gospel of Christ and when a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28837R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28837R\"></sup>door was opened for me in the Lord,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28838S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28838S\"></sup>had no rest for my spirit, not finding <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28838T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28838T\"></sup>Titus my brother; but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28838U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28838U\"></sup>taking my leave of them, I went on to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28838V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28838V\"></sup>Macedonia.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28839W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28839W\"></sup>But thanks be to God, who always <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28839X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28839X\"></sup>leads us in triumph in Christ, and manifests through us the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28839Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28839Y\"></sup>sweet aroma of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28839Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28839Z\"></sup>knowledge of Him in every place.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For we are a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28840AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28840AA\"></sup>fragrance of Christ to God among <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28840AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28840AB\"></sup>those who are being saved and among those who are perishing;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28841AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28841AC\"></sup>to the one an aroma from death to death, to the other an aroma from life to life. And who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28841AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28841AD\"></sup>adequate for these things?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For we are not like many, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28842AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28842AE\"></sup>peddling the word of God, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28842AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28842AF\"></sup>as from sincerity, but as from God, we speak in Christ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28842AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28842AG\"></sup>in the sight of God."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>Are we beginning to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28843A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28843A\"></sup>commend ourselves again? Or do we need, as some, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28843B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28843B\"></sup>letters of commendation to you or from you?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28844C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28844C\"></sup>You are our letter, written in our hearts, known and read by all men;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>being manifested that you are a letter of Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28845D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28845D\"></sup>cared for by us, written not with ink but with the Spirit of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28845E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28845E\"></sup>the living God, not on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28845F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28845F\"></sup>tablets of stone but on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28845G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28845G\"></sup>tablets of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28845H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28845H\"></sup>human hearts.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Such <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28846I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28846I\"></sup>confidence we have through Christ toward God.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Not that we are adequate in ourselves to consider anything as <i>coming</i> from ourselves, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28847J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28847J\"></sup>our adequacy is from God,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>who also made us adequate <i>as</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28848K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28848K\"></sup>servants of a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28848L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28848L\"></sup>new covenant, not of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28848M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28848M\"></sup>the letter but of the Spirit; for the letter kills, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28848N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28848N\"></sup>the Spirit gives life.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But if the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28849O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28849O\"></sup>ministry of death, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28849P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28849P\"></sup>in letters engraved on stones, came with glory, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28849Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28849Q\"></sup>so that the sons of Israel could not look intently at the face of Moses because of the glory of his face, fading <i>as</i> it was,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>how will the ministry of the Spirit fail to be even more with glory?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For if <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28851R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28851R\"></sup>the ministry of condemnation has glory, much more does the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28851S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28851S\"></sup>ministry of righteousness abound in glory.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For indeed what had glory, in this case has no glory because of the glory that surpasses <i>it</i>.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For if that which fades away <i>was</i> with glory, much more that which remains <i>is</i> in glory.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28854T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28854T\"></sup>Therefore having such a hope, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28854U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28854U\"></sup>we use great boldness in <i>our</i> speech,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>and <i>are</i> not like Moses, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28855V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28855V\"></sup><i>who</i> used to put a veil over his face so that the sons of Israel would not look intently at the end of what was fading away.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But their minds were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28856W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28856W\"></sup>hardened; for until this very day at the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28856X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28856X\"></sup>reading of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28856Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28856Y\"></sup>the old covenant the same veil remains unlifted, because it is removed in Christ.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But to this day whenever Moses is read, a veil lies over their heart;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28858Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28858Z\"></sup>but whenever a person turns to the Lord, the veil is taken away.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Now the Lord is the Spirit, and where <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28859AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28859AA\"></sup>the Spirit of the Lord is, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28859AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28859AB\"></sup><i>there</i> is liberty.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But we all, with unveiled face, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28860AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28860AC\"></sup>beholding as in a mirror the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28860AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28860AD\"></sup>glory of the Lord, are being <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28860AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28860AE\"></sup>transformed into the same image from glory to glory, just as from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28860AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28860AF\"></sup>the Lord, the Spirit."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>Therefore, since we have this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28861A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28861A\"></sup>ministry, as we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28861B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28861B\"></sup>received mercy, we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28861C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28861C\"></sup>do not lose heart,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>but we have renounced the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28862D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28862D\"></sup>things hidden because of shame, not walking in craftiness or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28862E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28862E\"></sup>adulterating the word of God, but by the manifestation of truth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28862F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28862F\"></sup>commending ourselves to every man’s conscience in the sight of God.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And even if our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28863G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28863G\"></sup>gospel is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28863H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28863H\"></sup>veiled, it is veiled to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28863I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28863I\"></sup>those who are perishing,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>in whose case <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28864J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28864J\"></sup>the god of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28864K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28864K\"></sup>this world has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28864L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28864L\"></sup>blinded the minds of the unbelieving so that they might not see the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28864M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28864M\"></sup>light of the gospel of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28864N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28864N\"></sup>glory of Christ, who is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28864O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28864O\"></sup>image of God.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28865P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28865P\"></sup>do not preach ourselves but Christ Jesus as Lord, and ourselves as your bond-servants for Jesus’ sake.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For God, who said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28866Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28866Q\"></sup>Light shall shine out of darkness,” is the One who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28866R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28866R\"></sup>shone in our hearts to give the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28866S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28866S\"></sup>Light of the knowledge of the glory of God in the face of Christ.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But we have this treasure in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28867T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28867T\"></sup>earthen vessels, so that the surpassing greatness of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28867U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28867U\"></sup>the power will be of God and not from ourselves;",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><i>we are</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28868V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28868V\"></sup>afflicted in every way, but not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28868W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28868W\"></sup>crushed; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28868X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28868X\"></sup>perplexed, but not despairing;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28869Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28869Y\"></sup>persecuted, but not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28869Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28869Z\"></sup>forsaken; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28869AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28869AA\"></sup>struck down, but not destroyed;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28870AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28870AB\"></sup>always carrying about in the body the dying of Jesus, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28870AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28870AC\"></sup>the life of Jesus also may be manifested in our body.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For we who live are constantly being delivered over to death for Jesus’ sake, so that the life of Jesus also may be manifested in our mortal flesh.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>So death works in us, but life in you.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But having the same <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28873AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28873AD\"></sup>spirit of faith, according to what is written, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28873AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28873AE\"></sup>I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">believed, therefore I spoke</span>,” we also believe, therefore we also speak,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>knowing that He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28874AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28874AF\"></sup>raised the Lord Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28874AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28874AG\"></sup>will raise us also with Jesus and will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28874AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28874AH\"></sup>present us with you.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For all things <i>are</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28875AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28875AI\"></sup>for your sakes, so that the grace which is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28875AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28875AJ\"></sup>spreading to more and more people may cause the giving of thanks to abound to the glory of God.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Therefore we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28876AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28876AK\"></sup>do not lose heart, but though our outer man is decaying, yet our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28876AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28876AL\"></sup>inner man is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28876AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28876AM\"></sup>being renewed day by day.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For momentary, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28877AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28877AN\"></sup>light affliction is producing for us an eternal weight of glory far beyond all comparison,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>while we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28878AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28878AO\"></sup>look not at the things which are seen, but at the things which are not seen; for the things which are seen are temporal, but the things which are not seen are eternal."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>For we know that if the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28879A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28879A\"></sup>earthly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28879B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28879B\"></sup>tent which is our house is torn down, we have a building from God, a house <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28879C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28879C\"></sup>not made with hands, eternal in the heavens.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For indeed in this <i>house</i> we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28880D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28880D\"></sup>groan, longing to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28880E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28880E\"></sup>clothed with our dwelling from heaven,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>inasmuch as we, having put it on, will not be found naked.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For indeed while we are in this tent, we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28882F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28882F\"></sup>groan, being burdened, because we do not want to be unclothed but to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28882G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28882G\"></sup>clothed, so that what is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28882H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28882H\"></sup>mortal will be swallowed up by life.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Now He who prepared us for this very purpose is God, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28883I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28883I\"></sup>gave to us the Spirit as a pledge.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Therefore, being always of good courage, and knowing that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28884J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28884J\"></sup>while we are at home in the body we are absent from the Lord—",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28885K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28885K\"></sup>we walk by faith, not by sight—",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>we are of good courage, I say, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28886L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28886L\"></sup>prefer rather to be absent from the body and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28886M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28886M\"></sup>to be at home with the Lord.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Therefore we also have as our ambition, whether at home or absent, to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28887N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28887N\"></sup>pleasing to Him.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For we must all appear before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28888O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28888O\"></sup>the judgment seat of Christ, so that each one may be recompensed for his deeds in the body, according to what he has done, whether good or bad.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Therefore, knowing the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28889P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28889P\"></sup>fear of the Lord, we persuade men, but we are made manifest to God; and I hope that we are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28889Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28889Q\"></sup>made manifest also in your consciences.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>We are not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28890R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28890R\"></sup>again commending ourselves to you but <i>are</i> giving you an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28890S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28890S\"></sup>occasion to be proud of us, so that you will have <i>an answer</i> for those who take pride in appearance and not in heart.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For if we are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28891T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28891T\"></sup>beside ourselves, it is for God; if we are of sound mind, it is for you.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For the love of Christ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28892U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28892U\"></sup>controls us, having concluded this, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28892V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28892V\"></sup>one died for all, therefore all died;",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>and He died for all, so that they who live might no longer <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28893W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28893W\"></sup>live for themselves, but for Him who died and rose again on their behalf.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Therefore from now on we recognize no one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28894X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28894X\"></sup>according to the flesh; even though we have known Christ according to the flesh, yet now we know <i>Him in this way</i> no longer.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Therefore if anyone is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28895Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28895Y\"></sup>in Christ, <i>he is</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28895Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28895Z\"></sup>a new creature; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28895AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28895AA\"></sup>the old things passed away; behold, new things have come.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28896AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28896AB\"></sup>all <i>these</i> things are from God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28896AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28896AC\"></sup>who reconciled us to Himself through Christ and gave us the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28896AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28896AD\"></sup>ministry of reconciliation,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>namely, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28897AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28897AE\"></sup>God was in Christ reconciling the world to Himself, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28897AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28897AF\"></sup>not counting their trespasses against them, and He has committed to us the word of reconciliation.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Therefore, we are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28898AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28898AG\"></sup>ambassadors for Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28898AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28898AH\"></sup>as though God were making an appeal through us; we beg you on behalf of Christ, be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28898AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28898AI\"></sup>reconciled to God.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>He made Him who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28899AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28899AJ\"></sup>knew no sin <i>to be</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28899AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28899AK\"></sup>sin on our behalf, so that we might become the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28899AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28899AL\"></sup>righteousness of God in Him."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28900A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28900A\"></sup>working together <i>with Him</i>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28900B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28900B\"></sup>we also urge you not to receive <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28900C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28900C\"></sup>the grace of God in vain—",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>for He says,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28901D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28901D\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">At the acceptable time I listened to you</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And on the day of salvation I helped you</span>.”Behold, now is “<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">the acceptable time</span>,” behold, now is “<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">the day of salvation</span>”—",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28902E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28902E\"></sup>giving no cause for offense in anything, so that the ministry will not be discredited,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>but in everything <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28903F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28903F\"></sup>commending ourselves as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28903G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28903G\"></sup>servants of God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28903H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28903H\"></sup>in much endurance, in afflictions, in hardships, in distresses,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28904I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28904I\"></sup>beatings, in imprisonments, in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28904J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28904J\"></sup>tumults, in labors, in sleeplessness, in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28904K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28904K\"></sup>hunger,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>in purity, in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28905L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28905L\"></sup>knowledge, in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28905M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28905M\"></sup>patience, in kindness, in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28905N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28905N\"></sup>Holy Spirit, in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28905O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28905O\"></sup>genuine love,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28906P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28906P\"></sup>the word of truth, in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28906Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28906Q\"></sup>the power of God; by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28906R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28906R\"></sup>the weapons of righteousness for the right hand and the left,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>by glory and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28907S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28907S\"></sup>dishonor, by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28907T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28907T\"></sup>evil report and good report; <i>regarded</i> as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28907U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28907U\"></sup>deceivers and yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28907V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28907V\"></sup>true;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>as unknown yet well-known, as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28908W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28908W\"></sup>dying yet behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28908X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28908X\"></sup>we live; as punished yet not put to death,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28909Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28909Y\"></sup>sorrowful yet always <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28909Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28909Z\"></sup>rejoicing, as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28909AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28909AA\"></sup>poor yet making many rich, as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28909AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28909AB\"></sup>having nothing yet possessing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28909AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28909AC\"></sup>all things.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28910AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28910AD\"></sup>Our mouth has spoken freely to you, O Corinthians, our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28910AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28910AE\"></sup>heart is opened wide.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>You are not restrained by us, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28911AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28911AF\"></sup>you are restrained in your own affections.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Now in a like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28912AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28912AG\"></sup>exchange—I speak as to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28912AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28912AH\"></sup>children—open wide <i>to us</i> also.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28913AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28913AI\"></sup>Do not be bound together with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28913AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28913AJ\"></sup>unbelievers; for what <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28913AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28913AK\"></sup>partnership have righteousness and lawlessness, or what fellowship has light with darkness?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Or what <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28914AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28914AL\"></sup>harmony has Christ with Belial, or what has a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28914AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28914AM\"></sup>believer in common with an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28914AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28914AN\"></sup>unbeliever?",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28915AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28915AO\"></sup>what agreement has the temple of God with idols? For we are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28915AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28915AP\"></sup>the temple of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28915AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28915AQ\"></sup>the living God; just as God said,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28915AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28915AR\"></sup>I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">will</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28915AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28915AS\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">dwell in them and</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28915AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28915AT\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">walk among them</span>;<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And I will be their God, and they shall be My people</span>.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28916AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28916AU\"></sup>Therefore, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28916AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28916AV\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">come out from their midst and be separate</span>,” says the Lord.“<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And do not touch what is unclean</span>;And I will welcome you.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28917AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28917AW\"></sup>And I will be a father to you,And you shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28917AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28917AX\"></sup>sons and daughters to Me,”Says the Lord Almighty."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>Therefore, having these promises, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28918A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28918A\"></sup>beloved, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28918B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28918B\"></sup>let us cleanse ourselves from all defilement of flesh and spirit, perfecting holiness in the fear of God.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28919C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28919C\"></sup>Make room for us <i>in your hearts</i>; we wronged no one, we corrupted no one, we took advantage of no one.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I do not speak to condemn you, for I have said <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28920D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28920D\"></sup>before that you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28920E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28920E\"></sup>in our hearts to die together and to live together.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Great is my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28921F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28921F\"></sup>confidence in you; great is my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28921G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28921G\"></sup>boasting on your behalf. I am filled with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28921H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28921H\"></sup>comfort; I am overflowing with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28921I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28921I\"></sup>joy in all our affliction.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For even when we came into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28922J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28922J\"></sup>Macedonia our flesh had no rest, but we were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28922K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28922K\"></sup>afflicted on every side: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28922L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28922L\"></sup>conflicts without, fears within.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28923M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28923M\"></sup>God, who comforts the depressed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28923N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28923N\"></sup>comforted us by the coming of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28923O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28923O\"></sup>Titus;",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>and not only by his coming, but also by the comfort with which he was comforted in you, as he reported to us your longing, your mourning, your zeal for me; so that I rejoiced even more.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For though I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28925P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28925P\"></sup>caused you sorrow by my letter, I do not regret it; though I did regret it—<i>for</i> I see that that letter caused you sorrow, though only for a while—",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I now rejoice, not that you were made sorrowful, but that you were made sorrowful to <i>the point of</i> repentance; for you were made sorrowful according to <i>the will of</i> God, so that you might not suffer loss in anything through us.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For the sorrow that is according to <i>the will of</i> God produces a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28927Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28927Q\"></sup>repentance without regret, <i>leading</i> to salvation, but the sorrow of the world produces death.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For behold what earnestness this very thing, this godly sorrow, has produced in you: what vindication of yourselves, what indignation, what fear, what <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28928R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28928R\"></sup>longing, what zeal, what <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28928S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28928S\"></sup>avenging of wrong! In everything you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28928T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28928T\"></sup>demonstrated yourselves to be innocent in the matter.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>So although <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28929U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28929U\"></sup>I wrote to you, <i>it was</i> not for the sake of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28929V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28929V\"></sup>the offender nor for the sake of the one offended, but that your earnestness on our behalf might be made known to you in the sight of God.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For this reason we have been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28930W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28930W\"></sup>comforted.And besides our comfort, we rejoiced even much more for the joy of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28930X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28930X\"></sup>Titus, because his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28930Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28930Y\"></sup>spirit has been refreshed by you all.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For if in anything I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28931Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28931Z\"></sup>boasted to him about you, I was not put to shame; but as we spoke all things to you in truth, so also our boasting before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28931AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28931AA\"></sup>Titus proved to be <i>the</i> truth.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>His affection abounds all the more toward you, as he remembers the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28932AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28932AB\"></sup>obedience of you all, how you received him with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28932AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28932AC\"></sup>fear and trembling.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I rejoice that in everything <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28933AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28933AD\"></sup>I have confidence in you."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>Now, brethren, we <i>wish to</i> make known to you the grace of God which has been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28934A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28934A\"></sup>given in the churches of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28934B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28934B\"></sup>Macedonia,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>that in a great ordeal of affliction their abundance of joy and their deep poverty overflowed in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28935C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28935C\"></sup>wealth of their liberality.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For I testify that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28936D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28936D\"></sup>according to their ability, and beyond their ability, <i>they gave</i> of their own accord,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>begging us with much urging for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28937E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28937E\"></sup>favor of participation in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28937F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28937F\"></sup>support of the saints,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>and <i>this</i>, not as we had expected, but they first <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28938G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28938G\"></sup>gave themselves to the Lord and to us by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28938H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28938H\"></sup>the will of God.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28939I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28939I\"></sup>urged <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28939J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28939J\"></sup>Titus that as he had previously <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28939K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28939K\"></sup>made a beginning, so he would also complete in you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28939L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28939L\"></sup>this gracious work as well.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But just as you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28940M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28940M\"></sup>abound <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28940N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28940N\"></sup>in everything, in faith and utterance and knowledge and in all earnestness and in the love we inspired in you, <i>see</i> that you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28940O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28940O\"></sup>abound in this gracious work also.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28941P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28941P\"></sup>am not speaking <i>this</i> as a command, but as proving through the earnestness of others the sincerity of your love also.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For you know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28942Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28942Q\"></sup>the grace of our Lord Jesus Christ, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28942R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28942R\"></sup>though He was rich, yet for your sake He became poor, so that you through His poverty might become rich.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28943S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28943S\"></sup>give <i>my</i> opinion in this matter, for this is to your advantage, who were the first to begin <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28943T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28943T\"></sup>a year ago not only to do <i>this</i>, but also to desire <i>to do it</i>.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But now finish doing it also, so that just as <i>there was</i> the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28944U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28944U\"></sup>readiness to desire it, so <i>there may be</i> also the completion of it by your ability.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For if the readiness is present, it is acceptable <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28945V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28945V\"></sup>according to what <i>a person</i> has, not according to what he does not have.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For <i>this</i> is not for the ease of others <i>and</i> for your affliction, but by way of equality—",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>at this present time your abundance <i>being a supply</i> for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28947W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28947W\"></sup>their need, so that their abundance also may become <i>a supply</i> for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28947X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28947X\"></sup>your need, that there may be equality;",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>as it is written, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28948Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28948Y\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">He who</span> <i>gathered</i> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">much did not have too much, and he who</span> <i>gathered</i> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">little had no lack</span>.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28949Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28949Z\"></sup>thanks be to God who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28949AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28949AA\"></sup>puts the same earnestness on your behalf in the heart of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28949AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28949AB\"></sup>Titus.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For he not only accepted our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28950AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28950AC\"></sup>appeal, but being himself very earnest, he has gone to you of his own accord.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>We have sent along with him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28951AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28951AD\"></sup>the brother whose fame in <i>the things of</i> the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28951AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28951AE\"></sup>gospel <i>has spread</i> through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28951AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28951AF\"></sup>all the churches;",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28952AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28952AG\"></sup>and not only <i>this</i>, but he has also been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28952AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28952AH\"></sup>appointed by the churches to travel with us in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28952AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28952AI\"></sup>this gracious work, which is being administered by us for the glory of the Lord Himself, and <i>to show</i> our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28952AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28952AJ\"></sup>readiness,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>taking precaution so that no one will discredit us in our administration of this generous gift;",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>for we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28954AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28954AK\"></sup>have regard for what is honorable, not only in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28954AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28954AL\"></sup>the sight of the Lord, but also in the sight of men.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>We have sent with them our brother, whom we have often tested and found diligent in many things, but now even more diligent because of <i>his</i> great confidence in you.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>As for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28956AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28956AM\"></sup>Titus, <i>he is</i> my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28956AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28956AN\"></sup>partner and fellow worker among you; as for our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28956AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28956AO\"></sup>brethren, <i>they are</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28956AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28956AP\"></sup>messengers of the churches, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28956AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28956AQ\"></sup>a glory to Christ.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Therefore openly before the churches, show them the proof of your love and of our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28957AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28957AR\"></sup>reason for boasting about you."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28958A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28958A\"></sup>it is superfluous for me to write to you about this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28958B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28958B\"></sup>ministry to the saints;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>for I know your readiness, of which I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28959C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28959C\"></sup>boast about you to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28959D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28959D\"></sup>Macedonians, <i>namely</i>, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28959E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28959E\"></sup>Achaia has been prepared since <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28959F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28959F\"></sup>last year, and your zeal has stirred up most of them.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But I have sent the brethren, in order that our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28960G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28960G\"></sup>boasting about you may not be made empty in this case, so that, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28960H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28960H\"></sup>as I was saying, you may be prepared;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>otherwise if any <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28961I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28961I\"></sup>Macedonians come with me and find you unprepared, we—not to speak of you—will be put to shame by this confidence.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>So I thought it necessary to urge the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28962J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28962J\"></sup>brethren that they would go on ahead to you and arrange beforehand your previously promised <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28962K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28962K\"></sup>bountiful gift, so that the same would be ready as a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28962L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28962L\"></sup>bountiful gift and not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28962M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28962M\"></sup>affected by covetousness.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Now this <i>I say</i>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28963N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28963N\"></sup>he who sows sparingly will also reap sparingly, and he who sows bountifully will also reap bountifully.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Each one <i>must do</i> just as he has purposed in his heart, not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28964O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28964O\"></sup>grudgingly or under compulsion, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28964P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28964P\"></sup>God loves a cheerful giver.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28965Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28965Q\"></sup>God is able to make all grace abound to you, so that always having all sufficiency in everything, you may have an abundance for every good deed;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>as it is written,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28966R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28966R\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">He scattered abroad, he gave to the poor</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">His righteousness</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">endures forever</span>.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Now He who supplies <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28967S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28967S\"></sup>seed to the sower and bread for food will supply and multiply your seed for sowing and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28967T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28967T\"></sup>increase the harvest of your righteousness;",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>you will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28968U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28968U\"></sup>enriched in everything for all liberality, which through us is producing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28968V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28968V\"></sup>thanksgiving to God.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For the ministry of this service is not only fully supplying <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28969W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28969W\"></sup>the needs of the saints, but is also overflowing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28969X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28969X\"></sup>through many thanksgivings to God.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Because of the proof given by this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28970Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28970Y\"></sup>ministry, they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28970Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28970Z\"></sup>glorify God for <i>your</i> obedience to your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28970AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28970AA\"></sup>confession of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28970AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28970AB\"></sup>gospel of Christ and for the liberality of your contribution to them and to all,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>while they also, by prayer on your behalf, yearn for you because of the surpassing grace of God in you.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28972AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28972AC\"></sup>Thanks be to God for His indescribable <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28972AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28972AD\"></sup>gift!"
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28973A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28973A\"></sup>I, Paul, myself <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28973B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28973B\"></sup>urge you by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28973C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28973C\"></sup>meekness and gentleness of Christ—I who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28973D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28973D\"></sup>am meek when face to face with you, but bold toward you when absent!",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I ask that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28974E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28974E\"></sup>when I am present I <i>need</i> not be bold with the confidence with which I propose to be courageous against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28974F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28974F\"></sup>some, who regard us as if we walked <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28974G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28974G\"></sup>according to the flesh.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For though we walk in the flesh, we do not war <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28975H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28975H\"></sup>according to the flesh,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28976I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28976I\"></sup>weapons of our warfare are not of the flesh, but divinely powerful <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28976J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28976J\"></sup>for the destruction of fortresses.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><i>We are</i> destroying speculations and every <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28977K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28977K\"></sup>lofty thing raised up against the knowledge of God, and <i>we are</i> taking every thought captive to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28977L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28977L\"></sup>obedience of Christ,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and we are ready to punish all disobedience, whenever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28978M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28978M\"></sup>your obedience is complete.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28979N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28979N\"></sup>You are looking at things as they are outwardly. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28979O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28979O\"></sup>If anyone is confident in himself that he is Christ’s, let him consider this again within himself, that just as he is Christ’s, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28979P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28979P\"></sup>so also are we.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For even if <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28980Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28980Q\"></sup>I boast somewhat further about our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28980R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28980R\"></sup>authority, which the Lord gave for building you up and not for destroying you, I will not be put to shame,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>for I do not wish to seem as if I would terrify you by my letters.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For they say, “His letters are weighty and strong, but his personal presence is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28982S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28982S\"></sup>unimpressive and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28982T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28982T\"></sup>his speech contemptible.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Let such a person consider this, that what we are in word by letters when absent, such persons <i>we are</i> also in deed when present.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For we are not bold to class or compare ourselves with some of those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28984U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28984U\"></sup>commend themselves; but when they measure themselves by themselves and compare themselves with themselves, they are without understanding.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But we will not boast <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28985V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28985V\"></sup>beyond <i>our</i> measure, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28985W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28985W\"></sup>within the measure of the sphere which God apportioned to us as a measure, to reach even as far as you.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For we are not overextending ourselves, as if we did not reach to you, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28986X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28986X\"></sup>we were the first to come even as far as you in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28986Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28986Y\"></sup>gospel of Christ;",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>not boasting <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28987Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28987Z\"></sup>beyond <i>our</i> measure, <i>that is</i>, in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28987AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28987AA\"></sup>other men’s labors, but with the hope that as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28987AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28987AB\"></sup>your faith grows, we will be, within our sphere, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28987AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28987AC\"></sup>enlarged even more by you,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>so as to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28988AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28988AD\"></sup>preach the gospel even to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28988AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28988AE\"></sup>the regions beyond you, <i>and</i> not to boast <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28988AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28988AF\"></sup>in what has been accomplished in the sphere of another.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28989AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28989AG\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">he who boasts is to boast in the Lord</span>.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For it is not he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28990AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28990AH\"></sup>commends himself that is approved, but he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28990AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28990AI\"></sup>whom the Lord commends."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>I wish that you would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28991A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28991A\"></sup>bear with me in a little <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28991B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28991B\"></sup>foolishness; but indeed you are bearing with me.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For I am jealous for you with a godly jealousy; for I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28992C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28992C\"></sup>betrothed you to one husband, so that to Christ I might <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28992D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28992D\"></sup>present you <i>as</i> a pure virgin.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But I am afraid that, as the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28993E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28993E\"></sup>serpent deceived Eve by his craftiness, your minds will be led astray from the simplicity and purity <i>of devotion</i> to Christ.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For if one comes and preaches <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28994F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28994F\"></sup>another Jesus whom we have not preached, or you receive a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28994G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28994G\"></sup>different spirit which you have not received, or a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28994H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28994H\"></sup>different gospel which you have not accepted, you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28994I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28994I\"></sup>bear <i>this</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28994J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28994J\"></sup>beautifully.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For I consider myself <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28995K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28995K\"></sup>not in the least inferior to the most eminent apostles.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But even if I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28996L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28996L\"></sup>unskilled in speech, yet I am not <i>so</i> in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28996M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28996M\"></sup>knowledge; in fact, in every way we have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28996N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28996N\"></sup>made <i>this</i> evident to you in all things.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28997O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28997O\"></sup>did I commit a sin in humbling myself so that you might be exalted, because I preached the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28997P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28997P\"></sup>gospel of God to you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28997Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28997Q\"></sup>without charge?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I robbed other churches by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28998R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28998R\"></sup>taking wages <i>from them</i> to serve you;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>and when I was present with you and was in need, I was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28999S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28999S\"></sup>not a burden to anyone; for when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28999T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28999T\"></sup>the brethren came from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28999U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28999U\"></sup>Macedonia they fully supplied my need, and in everything I kept myself from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-28999V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-28999V\"></sup>being a burden to you, and will continue to do so.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29000W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29000W\"></sup>As the truth of Christ is in me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29000X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29000X\"></sup>this boasting of mine will not be stopped in the regions of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29000Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29000Y\"></sup>Achaia.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Why? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29001Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29001Z\"></sup>Because I do not love you? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29001AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29001AA\"></sup>God knows <i>I do</i>!",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But what I am doing I will continue to do, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29002AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29002AB\"></sup>so that I may cut off opportunity from those who desire an opportunity to be regarded just as we are in the matter about which they are boasting.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For such men are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29003AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29003AC\"></sup>false apostles, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29003AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29003AD\"></sup>deceitful workers, disguising themselves as apostles of Christ.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>No wonder, for even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29004AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29004AE\"></sup>Satan disguises himself as an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29004AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29004AF\"></sup>angel of light.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Therefore it is not surprising if his servants also disguise themselves as servants of righteousness, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29005AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29005AG\"></sup>whose end will be according to their deeds.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29006AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29006AH\"></sup>Again I say, let no one think me foolish; but if <i>you do</i>, receive me even as foolish, so that I also may boast a little.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>What I am saying, I am not saying <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29007AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29007AI\"></sup>as the Lord would, but as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29007AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29007AJ\"></sup>in foolishness, in this confidence of boasting.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Since <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29008AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29008AK\"></sup>many boast <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29008AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29008AL\"></sup>according to the flesh, I will boast also.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29009AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29009AM\"></sup>being <i>so</i> wise, tolerate the foolish gladly.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For you tolerate it if anyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29010AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29010AN\"></sup>enslaves you, anyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29010AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29010AO\"></sup>devours you, anyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29010AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29010AP\"></sup>takes advantage of you, anyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29010AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29010AQ\"></sup>exalts himself, anyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29010AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29010AR\"></sup>hits you in the face.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>To <i>my</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29011AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29011AS\"></sup>shame I <i>must</i> say that we have been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29011AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29011AT\"></sup>weak <i>by comparison</i>.But in whatever respect anyone <i>else</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29011AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29011AU\"></sup>is bold—I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29011AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29011AV\"></sup>speak in foolishness—I am just as bold myself.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Are they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29012AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29012AW\"></sup>Hebrews? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29012AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29012AX\"></sup>So am I. Are they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29012AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29012AY\"></sup>Israelites? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29012AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29012AZ\"></sup>So am I. Are they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29012BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29012BA\"></sup>descendants of Abraham? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29012BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29012BB\"></sup>So am I.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Are they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29013BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29013BC\"></sup>servants of Christ?—I speak as if insane—I more so; in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29013BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29013BD\"></sup>far more labors, in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29013BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29013BE\"></sup>far more imprisonments, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29013BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29013BF\"></sup>beaten times without number, often in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29013BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29013BG\"></sup>danger of death.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Five times I received from the Jews <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29014BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29014BH\"></sup>thirty-nine <i>lashes</i>.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Three times I was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29015BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29015BI\"></sup>beaten with rods, once I was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29015BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29015BJ\"></sup>stoned, three times I was shipwrecked, a night and a day I have spent in the deep.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><i>I have been</i> on frequent journeys, in dangers from rivers, dangers from robbers, dangers from <i>my</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29016BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29016BK\"></sup>countrymen, dangers from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29016BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29016BL\"></sup>Gentiles, dangers in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29016BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29016BM\"></sup>city, dangers in the wilderness, dangers on the sea, dangers among <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29016BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29016BN\"></sup>false brethren;",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><i>I have been</i> in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29017BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29017BO\"></sup>labor and hardship, through many sleepless nights, in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29017BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29017BP\"></sup>hunger and thirst, often <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29017BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29017BQ\"></sup>without food, in cold and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29017BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29017BR\"></sup>exposure.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Apart from <i>such</i> external things, there is the daily pressure on me <i>of</i> concern for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29018BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29018BS\"></sup>all the churches.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29019BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29019BT\"></sup>weak without my being weak? Who is led into sin without my intense concern?",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>If I have to boast, I will boast of what pertains to my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29020BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29020BU\"></sup>weakness.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>The God and Father of the Lord Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29021BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29021BV\"></sup>He who is blessed forever, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29021BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29021BW\"></sup>knows that I am not lying.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>In <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29022BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29022BX\"></sup>Damascus the ethnarch under Aretas the king was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29022BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29022BY\"></sup>guarding the city of the Damascenes in order to seize me,",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>and I was let down in a basket <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29023BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29023BZ\"></sup>through a window in the wall, and <i>so</i> escaped his hands."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29024A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29024A\"></sup>Boasting is necessary, though it is not profitable; but I will go on to visions and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29024B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29024B\"></sup>revelations of the Lord.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I know a man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29025C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29025C\"></sup>in Christ who fourteen years ago—whether in the body I do not know, or out of the body I do not know, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29025D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29025D\"></sup>God knows—such a man was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29025E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29025E\"></sup>caught up to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29025F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29025F\"></sup>third heaven.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And I know how such a man—whether in the body or apart from the body I do not know, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29026G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29026G\"></sup>God knows—",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29027H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29027H\"></sup>caught up into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29027I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29027I\"></sup>Paradise and heard inexpressible words, which a man is not permitted to speak.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29028J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29028J\"></sup>On behalf of such a man I will boast; but on my own behalf I will not boast, except in regard to <i>my</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29028K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29028K\"></sup>weaknesses.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For if I do wish to boast I will not be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29029L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29029L\"></sup>foolish, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29029M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29029M\"></sup>for I will be speaking the truth; but I refrain <i>from this</i>, so that no one will credit me with more than he sees <i>in</i> me or hears from me.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Because of the surpassing greatness of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29030N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29030N\"></sup>revelations, for this reason, to keep me from exalting myself, there was given me a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29030O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29030O\"></sup>thorn in the flesh, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29030P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29030P\"></sup>messenger of Satan to torment me—to keep me from exalting myself!",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Concerning this I implored the Lord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29031Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29031Q\"></sup>three times that it might leave me.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And He has said to me, <span class=\"woj\">“My grace is sufficient for you, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29032R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29032R\"></sup>power is perfected in weakness.”</span> Most gladly, therefore, I will rather <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29032S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29032S\"></sup>boast about my weaknesses, so that the power of Christ may dwell in me.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29033T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29033T\"></sup>I am well content with weaknesses, with insults, with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29033U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29033U\"></sup>distresses, with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29033V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29033V\"></sup>persecutions, with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29033W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29033W\"></sup>difficulties, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29033X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29033X\"></sup>for Christ’s sake; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29033Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29033Y\"></sup>when I am weak, then I am strong.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I have become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29034Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29034Z\"></sup>foolish; you yourselves compelled me. Actually I should have been commended by you, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29034AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29034AA\"></sup>in no respect was I inferior to the most eminent apostles, even though <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29034AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29034AB\"></sup>I am a nobody.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29035AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29035AC\"></sup>signs of a true apostle were performed among you with all perseverance, by signs and wonders and miracles.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For in what respect were you treated as inferior to the rest of the churches, except that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29036AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29036AD\"></sup>I myself did not become a burden to you? Forgive me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29036AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29036AE\"></sup>this wrong!",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Here <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29037AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29037AF\"></sup>for this third time I am ready to come to you, and I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29037AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29037AG\"></sup>will not be a burden to you; for I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29037AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29037AH\"></sup>do not seek what is yours, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29037AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29037AI\"></sup>you; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29037AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29037AJ\"></sup>children are not responsible to save up for <i>their</i> parents, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29037AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29037AK\"></sup>parents for <i>their</i> children.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29038AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29038AL\"></sup>most gladly spend and be expended for your souls. If <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29038AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29038AM\"></sup>I love you more, am I to be loved less?",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But be that as it may, I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29039AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29039AN\"></sup>did not burden you myself; nevertheless, crafty fellow that I am, I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29039AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29039AO\"></sup>took you in by deceit.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29040AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29040AP\"></sup><i>Certainly</i> I have not taken advantage of you through any of those whom I have sent to you, have I?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29041AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29041AQ\"></sup>urged <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29041AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29041AR\"></sup>Titus <i>to go</i>, and I sent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29041AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29041AS\"></sup>the brother with him. Titus did not take any advantage of you, did he? Did we not conduct ourselves in the same <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29041AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29041AT\"></sup>spirit <i>and walk</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29041AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29041AU\"></sup>in the same steps?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>All this time you have been thinking that we are defending ourselves to you. <i>Actually</i>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29042AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29042AV\"></sup>it is in the sight of God that we have been speaking in Christ; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29042AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29042AW\"></sup>all for your upbuilding, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29042AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29042AX\"></sup>beloved.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For I am afraid that perhaps <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29043AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29043AY\"></sup>when I come I may find you to be not what I wish and may be found by you to be not what you wish; that perhaps <i>there will be</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29043AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29043AZ\"></sup>strife, jealousy, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29043BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29043BA\"></sup>angry tempers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29043BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29043BB\"></sup>disputes, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29043BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29043BC\"></sup>slanders, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29043BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29043BD\"></sup>gossip, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29043BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29043BE\"></sup>arrogance, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29043BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29043BF\"></sup>disturbances;",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I am afraid that when I come again my God may humiliate me before you, and I may mourn over many of those who have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29044BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29044BG\"></sup>sinned in the past and not repented of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29044BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29044BH\"></sup>impurity, immorality and sensuality which they have practiced."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29045A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29045A\"></sup>This is the third time I am coming to you. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29045B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29045B\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Every</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">fact</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">is to be confirmed by the</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">testimony of two or three witnesses</span>.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I have previously said when present the second time, and though now absent I say in advance to those who have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29046C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29046C\"></sup>sinned in the past and to all the rest <i>as well</i>, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29046D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29046D\"></sup>if I come again I will not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29046E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29046E\"></sup>spare <i>anyone</i>,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>since you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29047F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29047F\"></sup>seeking for proof of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29047G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29047G\"></sup>Christ who speaks in me, and who is not weak toward you, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29047H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29047H\"></sup>mighty in you.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For indeed He was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29048I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29048I\"></sup>crucified because of weakness, yet He lives <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29048J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29048J\"></sup>because of the power of God. For we also are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29048K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29048K\"></sup>weak in Him, yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29048L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29048L\"></sup>we will live with Him because of the power of God <i>directed</i> toward you.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29049M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29049M\"></sup>Test yourselves <i>to see</i> if you are in the faith; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29049N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29049N\"></sup>examine yourselves! Or do you not recognize this about yourselves, that Jesus Christ is in you—unless indeed you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29049O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29049O\"></sup>fail the test?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But I trust that you will realize that we ourselves do not fail the test.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Now we pray to God that you do no wrong; not that we ourselves may appear approved, but that you may do what is right, even though we may appear unapproved.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For we can do nothing against the truth, but <i>only</i> for the truth.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For we rejoice when we ourselves are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29053P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29053P\"></sup>weak but you are strong; this we also pray for, that you be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29053Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29053Q\"></sup>made complete.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For this reason I am writing these things while absent, so that when present <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29054R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29054R\"></sup>I <i>need</i> not use <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29054S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29054S\"></sup>severity, in accordance with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29054T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29054T\"></sup>authority which the Lord gave me for building up and not for tearing down.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29055U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29055U\"></sup>Finally, brethren, rejoice, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29055V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29055V\"></sup>be made complete, be comforted, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29055W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29055W\"></sup>be like-minded, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29055X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29055X\"></sup>live in peace; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29055Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29055Y\"></sup>the God of love and peace will be with you.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29056Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29056Z\"></sup>Greet one another with a holy kiss.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29057AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29057AA\"></sup>All the saints greet you.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29058AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29058AB\"></sup>The grace of the Lord Jesus Christ, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29058AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29058AC\"></sup>love of God, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29058AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29058AD\"></sup>fellowship of the Holy Spirit, be with you all."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;